messages.content: You are tasked with creating a structured output from the provided user message.

Files containing the handler implementation
- app/Http/Controllers/Admin/PostThumbnailController.php

Explanation
- routes/admin.php registers the route Route::delete('/posts/{post}/thumbnail', [PostThumbnailController::class, 'destroy']) which maps to App\Http\Controllers\Admin\PostThumbnailController::destroy.
- I searched the project for the controller class and found the implementation at the path above.
- The destroy method implementation (in that file) updates the given Post by setting thumbnail_id to null and then redirects to the admin.posts.edit route with a success flash message. Tests and unrelated files were ignored.
